Rajavelu told me about this thumbnail, and
said he couldn’t understand this thumbnail.

00:05:24.260 --> 00:05:28.130
Looks like there is a knife through your heart,
there is a lot of bleeding…

00:05:28.130 --> 00:05:30.770
I understood the video, once I watched it,
but the thumbnail, I couldn’t grasp it…

00:05:30.770 --> 00:05:31.770
he said.

