Surya Krishna wrote a long note to me.

00:11:04.390 --> 00:11:06.590
Please find the time to read it at leisure.

00:11:06.590 --> 00:11:11.460
But, it was basically about “Many people
have said many things about your Quotidians!

00:11:11.460 --> 00:11:14.550
But, I would like to tell you about your thumbnails.

00:11:14.550 --> 00:11:16.110
They are really interesting.

00:11:16.110 --> 00:11:17.110
Thanks a lot.”

00:11:17.110 --> 00:11:20.190
And he continued, “This video had a thumbnail.

00:11:20.190 --> 00:11:23.030
A shaved head sprouted a hair style!

00:11:23.030 --> 00:11:28.420
You had a beautiful girl to pose along with
you too!”

00:11:28.420 --> 00:11:36.360
That was when I realised that probably you
are all too young, or probably I am too old,

00:11:36.360 --> 00:11:39.660
and I am referring to a very old movie..

00:11:39.660 --> 00:11:42.920
In fact, the first movie featuring John Travolta.

00:11:42.920 --> 00:11:43.920
Called Grease.

00:11:43.920 --> 00:11:51.980
Perhaps it was this movie, Grease, that was
one of the first teenage love movies that

00:11:51.980 --> 00:11:55.460
became such a roaring hit on the big screen.

00:11:55.460 --> 00:11:57.810
Watch it if you get the time.

00:11:57.810 --> 00:12:00.110
An interesting movie with a lot of good songs.

00:12:00.110 --> 00:12:04.580
And, it was from this movie that I picked
up the idea for the thumbnail.

00:12:04.580 --> 00:12:05.580
Why?

00:12:05.580 --> 00:12:06.580
Well..

00:12:06.580 --> 00:12:07.580
Grease.

00:12:07.580 --> 00:12:08.580
That means Frictionless.

00:12:08.580 --> 00:12:09.580
I hope you get the connection.

00:12:09.580 --> 00:12:12.730
Varadarasan appreciated me for the concept
of the Desire Path.

00:12:12.730 --> 00:12:15.970
And, he brought in a deeply philosophical
analogy from family life.

00:12:15.970 --> 00:12:23.170
He quipped that it was applicable even at
home where the wife and the mother-in-law

00:12:23.170 --> 00:12:30.600
can actually work it out if only there was
an accommodation of the Desire Path.

00:12:30.600 --> 00:12:33.839
I thought about it a bit more.

00:12:33.839 --> 00:12:34.839
Such an interesting thought.

00:12:34.839 --> 00:12:35.990
Let us take it further.

00:12:35.990 --> 00:12:42.670
And that was when it occurred to me — If
we were to implement the Desire Path at home

00:12:42.670 --> 00:12:48.660
soon after the wedding, we should pack off
the mother-in-law and the father-in-law, or

00:12:48.660 --> 00:12:52.630
rather the boy’s parents on a honeymoon.

00:12:52.630 --> 00:12:54.990
Please leave the house.

00:12:54.990 --> 00:13:00.840
By the time you are back, the house would
have a Desire Path.

00:13:00.840 --> 00:13:02.740
Of this girl who had just come in.

00:13:02.740 --> 00:13:09.460
And that is how things should be, if you want
marital bliss.

00:13:09.460 --> 00:13:11.080
Think about it!

00:13:11.080 --> 00:13:17.270
Vignesh Shankar told me — Now I get what
passion really means.

00:13:17.270 --> 00:13:20.870
You launched one video every day consistently,
now I understand.

00:13:20.870 --> 00:13:21.870
You have a commitment.

00:13:21.870 --> 00:13:23.680
You want to pass it on.

00:13:23.680 --> 00:13:24.680
Yes.

00:13:24.680 --> 00:13:25.680
Yes.

00:13:25.680 --> 00:13:26.680
Yes.

00:13:26.680 --> 00:13:27.680
Yes.

00:13:27.680 --> 00:13:28.680
But..

00:13:28.680 --> 00:13:30.160
There was one more revelation that I had.

00:13:30.160 --> 00:13:35.370
This thing they repeat often “Do it with
passion”, “Do it with passion”… many

00:13:35.370 --> 00:13:38.360
people have given many definitions over the
years, to this Passion-word.

00:13:38.360 --> 00:13:39.360
I got one.

00:13:39.360 --> 00:13:42.620
One could even say I learned it the hard way.

00:13:42.620 --> 00:13:46.920
And, this is MY definition for passion.

00:13:46.920 --> 00:13:48.720
And it goes like this.

00:13:48.720 --> 00:13:58.010
It says, “It is the ability to be at it,
even when you are not good at it, yet!”

00:13:58.010 --> 00:14:08.180
Even if you are not an expert at it, even
when you are still learning the ropes, the

00:14:08.180 --> 00:14:12.940
feeling that you will get it some day, that
you will become an expert at it some day,

00:14:12.940 --> 00:14:18.950
and I have the stamina and willpower to pull
through till that day, probably that is passion!

00:14:18.950 --> 00:14:24.330
Probably that is the pain, suffering, struggle,
the Jesus Christ reference that we saw earlier?

00:14:24.330 --> 00:14:29.740
To be at it even when you are not good at
it yet!

00:14:29.740 --> 00:14:34.730
That perhaps is passion!

00:14:34.730 --> 00:14:39.480
One friend commented to me that this word
Mentor — I didn’t know that it was really

00:14:39.480 --> 00:14:41.320
about a person…

00:14:41.320 --> 00:14:44.750
Thanks a lot, that’s so useful, he said!

00:14:44.750 --> 00:14:49.210
I am gonna burst his bubble a wee bit, I am
sorry.

00:14:49.210 --> 00:14:54.230
Because, the information I gave you was not
“complete”.

00:14:54.230 --> 00:14:58.740
I had told you the story of Telemachus, the
son of Ulysses, and this person called Mentor,

00:14:58.740 --> 00:15:05.290
this old man was assigned to take care of
the boy and the story went well, or so we

00:15:05.290 --> 00:15:06.290
thought.

00:15:06.290 --> 00:15:07.800
Sorry, the story DIDN’T go well!

00:15:07.800 --> 00:15:15.029
That old man was a drunkard, he wasted time,
slept all day, Telemachus suffered without

00:15:15.029 --> 00:15:16.790
a mentor!

00:15:16.790 --> 00:15:26.680
And, that’s when one of the favorite Gods
in Greek Mythology, favorite Gods of Ulysses,

00:15:26.680 --> 00:15:33.120
the Goddess of Learning, Literature, Arts,
Warfare, a direct daughter of Zeus himself,

00:15:33.120 --> 00:15:44.110
Athena by name, she, one of the skills she
had was the ability to shape-shift.

00:15:44.110 --> 00:15:51.580
She became the old man, Mentor, and mentored
Telemachus!

00:15:51.580 --> 00:15:53.870
So, all the women out there!

00:15:53.870 --> 00:16:02.250
You can be truly proud and happy that the
first ever mentor was a woman!

00:16:02.250 --> 00:16:08.640
In fact, if you roll back in time, I talked
about this on International Women’s Day,

00:16:08.640 --> 00:16:11.370
Happy International Women’s Day!

00:16:11.370 --> 00:16:12.370
Thanks then!

